quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,Basi nguilumbila yankuiwona
  69,39,Ni yangankuiwona
  69,40,Chisimu jalakwe (Qur'aniji) liŵele liloŵe lya Ntenga Jwakuchimbichika (Jibulilu)
  69,41,"Ni nganijiŵa jalakwejo liloŵe lya nkwimba chilaanga, yannonope ni yankuikulupilila"
  69,42,"Soni ngaŵa liloŵe lya abimbi, yannonope ni yankukumbuchila"
  69,43,(Jiŵele) jakutulusyidwa kuumila kwa M'mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  69,44,Soni ingaŵe kuti (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwalukenye Kukwetu unami winewakwe
  69,45,Chisimu tukankwembekenye mwamachili
  69,46,Kaneka nitukakatile kwene mwa jwalakwejo ntasi (wakwe waumi nikuwa)
  69,47,Mwanti nga nganapatikana jwalijose mwa jenumanja jwakun'gosa (ku ipotesi Yetu)
  69,48,Soni chisimu jalakwe (Qur’ani) jiŵele chikumbusyo kwa ŵakun'jogopa (Allah)
  69,49,Sonitu Uwwe tukumanyilila kusyene yanti mwa ŵanganyammwe mwana ŵakanila
  69,50,Soni chisimu jalakwe (Qur’ani) jichiŵa jakwadandaulikasya kusyene achimakafili (ku Kiyama ndema jatachiuwona ntendele wa ŵajikuya ni ipotesi ya ŵajikana)
  69,51,Soni chisimu jalakweji jiŵele jakuona kusyesyene
  69,52,Basi liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu Ŵakuchimbichika nnope